APL Open Source Software Agreement

AMH PUBLIC LICENSE Open Source Software Agreement (V1.1)

Open source software agreement applicable to free licensing or commercial operation development

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Introduction to APL open source software protocol

In order to effectively protect the transparency, purity, security and stability of the software used by users and the relevant rights and interests of users,

At the same time, it can better contribute to the sustainable development of domestic open source software. The AMH official website drafted the following open source software agreement, named APL open source software agreement.

The APL open source software agreement will be committed to promoting software transparency, open source innovation and development, advocating perfectionism, focusing on quality, and calling for respect for original copyright, and promoting the spirit of abiding by the contract.




The following agreements are abbreviated

Software product developer: software official

User of software product: user




APL open source software agreement



The software officially complies with the agreement

1) It is prohibited to publish source code programs in closed source, and all users of source code programs can read them.

2) The complete source code program must be provided in any way, such as online download, CD and disk copy.

3) Transparent source code programs must be provided. It is prohibited to use any reversible or irreversible means to confuse source code programs.

4) Any infringement is prohibited, including the source code program, data files and file information of the software.

5) It is prohibited to insert any advertising information, including text, image and media information, that is not related to the official software.

6) It is prohibited to build any third-party plug-ins and components that are not related to the official application of the software.

7) The software program is prohibited from having any control program that is executed by remote response without the permission of the user.

8) Software programs are prohibited from using any means to collect user privacy information and data stored by users.




Users comply with the agreement

1) Users of the software must comply with the national laws and regulations of the People's Republic of China.

2) Users are prohibited from modifying any official copyright description information of the software, including the copyright agreement description of the program, official software link, text description, image logo, and media information.

3) Users are prohibited from destroying or infringing the normal development and operation of the official software program in any way, including the normal operation of the official software program and the commercial authorization mechanism.




Statement on the use and effectiveness of the agreement

The software official who uses the APL open source software agreement should indicate the use of the APL open source software agreement and the accompanying agreement documentation in the source code program comments,

The agreement will take effect immediately after the user installs the software using the APL open source agreement.




