Join the APL open source software agreement

If you are the software official and can reach a consensus with the APL agreement and have the common will with us,

Welcome to join the APL open source software agreement.




Use of APL open source software protocol

1) The APL open source software protocol is used for program source file annotation.

/************************************************

*Software source code description and other information

*

* @license APL ( http://amh.sh/apl.htm ) V1.1

*

*/



2) Download the APL open source software protocol file license.txt and release it with the source program file.








