Investigation for breach of contract

The software official and the software user must abide by every clause of the agreement,

If the software official or user violates any of the terms of this agreement, the party who abides by the agreement will have the right to immediately stop providing services and have the right to investigate the legal and criminal responsibilities of the breaching party according to law.



In case of default of software official or software user,

Please contact us to submit the case description and provide the archived script program and analysis data that are effective for review. The AMH official website will assist in follow-up.



